reviewText: I loved this movie when my kids were little. Love it know that I have Grand kids. Diffently a movie for kids.
this was everything i hoped it would be. oh, the waves of nostalgia it released!! it was a great surprise for my family too. the vhs was in excellent condition and i am 100% satisfied.

This is a wonderful children's video.  The story captivates young and old alike and although the claymation is not smooth, it does provide a good visual.  The songs are a nice touch to the story.  I would like to get a personal copy of this video.
